4 weeks ago - Trinity Racing is a British multi-discipline cycling team, that has competed in road, cyclo-cross and mountain bike racing. It was founded in 2018 as a cyclo-cross team, before expanding into road cycling in 2020, and mountain biking in 2021. The road team closed down at the end of the 2024 season.
